Package com.CZ2002.exceptions

package com.CZ2002.exceptions
Provides the Exception classes used in the application.

This package contains the necessary implementations of Exception used to denote when an exception is encountered in the application.

The exceptions defined in this package are specific to the application and mainly relate to the possible options taken in the consoles.
